{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind","slug":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind","title":"The River That Changed Its Mind","title_ko":"마음을 바꾼 강","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/cover.webp","summary_ko":"오래 흐르던 길을 바꾼 강 때문에 마을이 함께 새 물길을 내며 다시 어우러지는 따뜻한 이야기예요.","wordCount":271,"pages":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"For a hundred years the river ran beside the village.","translation_ko":"백 년 동안 강은 마을 곁을 따라 흘렀어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"For","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"a","charStart":4,"charEnd":5,"startMs":240,"endMs":480},{"word":"hundred","charStart":6,"charEnd":13,"startMs":480,"endMs":860},{"word":"years","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":860,"endMs":1300},{"word":"the","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1520},{"word":"river","charStart":24,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1760},{"word":"ran","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2180},{"word":"beside","charStart":34,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2620},{"word":"the","charStart":41,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2800},{"word":"village","charStart":45,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2800,"endMs":3120}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"It curved past the houses like a shining blue ribbon.","translation_ko":"강은 반짝이는 푸른 리본처럼 집들 옆을 굽이쳐 지나갔지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"curved","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":340,"endMs":760},{"word":"past","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":760,"endMs":1300},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1640},{"word":"houses","charStart":19,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1880},{"word":"like","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2320},{"word":"a","charStart":31,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2900},{"word":"shining","charStart":33,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2900,"endMs":2900},{"word":"blue","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3340},{"word":"ribbon","charStart":46,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3340,"endMs":3560}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Children splashed in the cool water every summer.","translation_ko":"여름이면 아이들은 시원한 물에서 첨벙거리며 놀았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Children","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"splashed","charStart":9,"charEnd":17,"startMs":560,"endMs":1080},{"word":"in","charStart":18,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1220},{"word":"the","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1460},{"word":"cool","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1640},{"word":"water","charStart":30,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1940},{"word":"every","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2440},{"word":"summer","charStart":42,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2680}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Farmers filled their buckets, and the gardens grew green.","translation_ko":"농부들은 양동이에 물을 채웠고, 텃밭은 푸르게 자랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Farmers","charStart":0,"charEnd":7,"startMs":0,"endMs":600},{"word":"filled","charStart":8,"charEnd":14,"startMs":600,"endMs":860},{"word":"their","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":860,"endMs":1140},{"word":"buckets","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1480},{"word":"and","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2000},{"word":"the","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2260},{"word":"gardens","charStart":38,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2440},{"word":"grew","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2780},{"word":"green","charStart":51,"charEnd":56,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3100}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"But a river is always thinking, even when it looks still.","translation_ko":"하지만 강은 잔잔해 보일 때에도 늘 무언가를 생각하고 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"a","charStart":4,"charEnd":5,"startMs":300,"endMs":600},{"word":"river","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":600,"endMs":840},{"word":"is","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":840,"endMs":1140},{"word":"always","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1640},{"word":"thinking","charStart":22,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2020},{"word":"even","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2700,"endMs":2780},{"word":"when","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2780,"endMs":2940},{"word":"it","charStart":42,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3080},{"word":"looks","charStart":45,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3300},{"word":"still","charStart":51,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3620}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"Slowly, quietly, it began to change its mind.","translation_ko":"강은 천천히, 조용히 마음을 바꾸기 시작했지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Slowly","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":800},{"word":"quietly","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1600},{"word":"it","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2420},{"word":"began","charStart":20,"charEnd":25,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2700},{"word":"to","charStart":26,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3220},{"word":"change","charStart":29,"charEnd":35,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3240},{"word":"its","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":3240,"endMs":3520},{"word":"mind","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3520,"endMs":3820}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"Each spring it pushed a little farther from the houses.","translation_ko":"봄마다 강은 집들에게서 조금씩 더 멀어졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Each","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"spring","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":740,"endMs":1100},{"word":"it","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1420},{"word":"pushed","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1640},{"word":"a","charStart":22,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1840},{"word":"little","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2040},{"word":"farther","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2320},{"word":"from","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2600},{"word":"the","charStart":44,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2800},{"word":"houses","charStart":48,"charEnd":54,"startMs":2800,"endMs":3040}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Inch by inch, the water wandered toward the hills.","translation_ko":"강물은 조금씩 조금씩 언덕 쪽으로 흘러갔답니다.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Inch","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":500},{"word":"by","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":500,"endMs":740},{"word":"inch","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":740,"endMs":1080},{"word":"the","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1640},{"word":"water","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1960},{"word":"wandered","charStart":24,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2440},{"word":"toward","charStart":33,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2740},{"word":"the","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3260},{"word":"hills","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3260}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"One morning the villagers woke to dry, cracked ground.","translation_ko":"어느 아침, 마을 사람들은 메마르고 갈라진 땅을 보며 잠에서 깼어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"morning","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":340,"endMs":740},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":960,"endMs":1140},{"word":"villagers","charStart":16,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1520},{"word":"woke","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1820},{"word":"to","charStart":31,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2120},{"word":"dry","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2580},{"word":"cracked","charStart":39,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2980,"endMs":2980},{"word":"ground","charStart":47,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2980,"endMs":3440}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"The old riverbed was empty, and the wells ran low.","translation_ko":"옛 강바닥은 텅 비었고, 우물물도 줄어들었지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"old","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":440,"endMs":840},{"word":"riverbed","charStart":8,"charEnd":16,"startMs":840,"endMs":1320},{"word":"was","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1600},{"word":"empty","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1880},{"word":"and","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2620},{"word":"the","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2940},{"word":"wells","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3100},{"word":"ran","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3420},{"word":"low","charStart":46,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3420,"endMs":3700}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"The children missed the laughter of the water.","translation_ko":"아이들은 물이 내던 웃음 같은 소리를 그리워했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"children","charStart":4,"charEnd":12,"startMs":200,"endMs":560},{"word":"missed","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":560,"endMs":860},{"word":"the","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":860,"endMs":1320},{"word":"laughter","charStart":24,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1440},{"word":"of","charStart":33,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1600},{"word":"the","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1760},{"word":"water","charStart":40,"charEnd":45,"startMs":1760,"endMs":1940}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Why did the river leave us?\" they asked sadly.","translation_ko":"\"강은 왜 우리를 떠났을까?\" 아이들이 슬프게 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Why","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"did","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":460,"endMs":720},{"word":"the","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":720,"endMs":980},{"word":"river","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":980,"endMs":1120},{"word":"leave","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1420},{"word":"us","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1760},{"word":"they","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2260},{"word":"asked","charStart":35,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2560},{"word":"sadly","charStart":41,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2940}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"An old woman smiled and shook her grey head.","translation_ko":"한 할머니가 미소 지으며 흰머리를 가만히 저었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"An","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"old","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":180,"endMs":560},{"word":"woman","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":560,"endMs":820},{"word":"smiled","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":820,"endMs":1300},{"word":"and","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1640},{"word":"shook","charStart":24,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1760},{"word":"her","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1760,"endMs":1980},{"word":"grey","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2240},{"word":"head","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2440}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"A river does not leave,\" she said. \"It only looks for a new way.\"","translation_ko":"\"강은 떠나는 게 아니란다. 그저 새 길을 찾는 거야.\" 할머니가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":640},{"word":"river","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":640,"endMs":820},{"word":"does","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":820,"endMs":1100},{"word":"not","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1340},{"word":"leave","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1620},{"word":"she","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2060},{"word":"said","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2300},{"word":"It","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2880},{"word":"only","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3160},{"word":"looks","charStart":45,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3380},{"word":"for","charStart":51,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3600},{"word":"a","charStart":55,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3600,"endMs":3760},{"word":"new","charStart":57,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3760,"endMs":3900},{"word":"way","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":3900,"endMs":4100}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"So the whole village walked out to meet the wandering water.","translation_ko":"그래서 온 마을 사람들이 길을 떠난 강물을 만나러 걸어 나갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"the","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":240,"endMs":400},{"word":"whole","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":400,"endMs":760},{"word":"village","charStart":13,"charEnd":20,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"walked","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1360},{"word":"out","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1620},{"word":"to","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1840},{"word":"meet","charStart":35,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1840,"endMs":1940},{"word":"the","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2160},{"word":"wandering","charStart":44,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2520},{"word":"water","charStart":54,"charEnd":59,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2900}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"They carried shovels, baskets, and a quiet kind of hope.","translation_ko":"사람들은 삽과 바구니, 그리고 조용한 희망을 함께 들고 갔지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"carried","charStart":5,"charEnd":12,"startMs":380,"endMs":820},{"word":"shovels","charStart":13,"charEnd":20,"startMs":820,"endMs":1680},{"word":"baskets","charStart":22,"charEnd":29,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2220},{"word":"and","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2780,"endMs":2860},{"word":"a","charStart":35,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2860,"endMs":3140},{"word":"quiet","charStart":37,"charEnd":42,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3320},{"word":"kind","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3600},{"word":"of","charStart":48,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3600,"endMs":3960},{"word":"hope","charStart":51,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3960,"endMs":3960}]}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"Together they dug a gentle new channel through the field.","translation_ko":"사람들은 힘을 모아 들판을 가로지르는 부드러운 새 물길을 팠어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Together","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":740,"endMs":1200},{"word":"they","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1520},{"word":"dug","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1680},{"word":"a","charStart":18,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1900},{"word":"gentle","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2180},{"word":"new","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2440},{"word":"channel","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2680},{"word":"through","charStart":39,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2680,"endMs":2940},{"word":"the","charStart":47,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3120},{"word":"field","charStart":51,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3120,"endMs":3360}]},{"id":"the-river-that-changed-its-mind-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"When they grew tired, they shared bread and rested in the shade.","translation_ko":"지칠 때면 빵을 나눠 먹고 그늘에서 쉬었답니다.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-river-that-changed-its-mind/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"they","charStart"